main event: Two unidentified objects were sighted moving east near Orlando, Florida on July 14, 1955.
interesting points: The sighting involved two objects reportedly moving rapidly and weaving slightly through the sky., The objects were first seen around 1:45 PM and were noted to be bright lights., The observation lasted for approximately 2 minutes according to the witnesses., Witnesses included civilians who were notified to look towards the Florida skies., Weather conditions during the sighting were clear, providing a good view of the objects.
sighted object: two unidentified flying objects in the sky
